      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Here's an honest, no-nonsense opportunity for a budget-conscious buyer! This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it runs and gets you where you need to go, but it does show more wear than a typical used car and may benefit from some attention down the road. It's priced accordingly so you're getting real value for what you're paying. If you're handy, looking for a project, or just need reliable transportation without breaking the bank, this could be a great fit!",
