    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in fair condition, and the price has been set honestly to reflect its current state \u2014 please read the full description before reaching out. The car runs and drives, making it a practical option for a buyer who understands they're getting a used vehicle with some wear and age. Expect typical cosmetic imperfections such as minor dents, scratches, or faded trim, along with the kind of mechanical wear you'd anticipate from a vehicle that has seen regular use. It is not in showroom shape, but it is functional and has not been dressed up or misrepresented to attract attention. There are no major structural or safety concerns that would prevent daily use, but a pre-purchase inspection by a trusted mechanic is always encouraged and welcomed. This is an honest listing for a buyer looking for reliable transportation at a fair price, without paying a premium for cosmetics or extras.",
