      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in mint condition \u2014 a truly exceptional find in the used car market. The exterior is virtually flawless, with paint that retains its deep, original luster and bodywork free of dents, scratches, or blemishes of any significance. Every panel aligns perfectly, and the chrome and trim elements shine as though the car just rolled off the showroom floor. The interior is equally impressive: the upholstery shows no meaningful wear, all surfaces are clean and unmarked, and every control, button, and feature functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is in outstanding shape \u2014 the engine runs smoothly and powerfully, all systems operate without issue, and there are no warning lights or known mechanical concerns whatsoever. This is the kind of used car that rarely comes to market in this state of preservation, and it represents a genuine opportunity for a buyer who wants near-new quality without the new-car price tag.",
